<mvc:View controllerName="test.Sample.controller.Main" 
	displayBlock="true" 
	xmlns="sap.m" 
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
	xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns:u="sap.ui.unified">
	<Page title="{i18n>appTitle}">
		<headerContent>
			<core:Icon color="#1873B4" 
				src="sap-icon://sap-ui5" 
				size="2rem"/>
		</headerContent>
		<content>
			<l:BlockLayout background="Light">
				<l:BlockLayoutRow>
					<l:BlockLayoutCell>
						<Title level="H1" 
							titleStyle="H1" 
							text="{i18n>startPage.title.text}" 
							width="100%" 
							textAlign="Center" />
					</l:BlockLayoutCell>
				</l:BlockLayoutRow>
				<l:BlockLayoutRow>
					<l:BlockLayoutCell>
						<u:FileUploader></u:FileUploader>

					</l:BlockLayoutCell>
				</l:BlockLayoutRow>
				<l:BlockLayoutRow>
					<l:BlockLayoutCell>
						<List headerText="{i18n>startpage.list.headerText}">

						</List>
					</l:BlockLayoutCell>
					<l:BlockLayoutCell>
						<Text text="preview" />
					</l:BlockLayoutCell>
				</l:BlockLayoutRow>

			</l:BlockLayout>
		</content>
	</Page>

</mvc:View>